abstract: >
  A public-safe, high-impact playbook for controlling AI assistants (including coding agents) in real work:
  failure mode taxonomy (FM-01..FM-40), operational controls (Control OS), a shareable incident ledger format,
  and a 4+1 layer quality system design. Based on 14 days of hands-on governance with Claude Code.
